  "title": "Digital Sales Representative (Basic + Comms | Banking)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Work location: CBP (Expo)/Central</li><li>Leads will be provided</li><li>Basic salary + commissions (of up to $5000)</li><li>Training will be provided</li></ul><p><strong>The Job</strong> </p><ul><li>Promote, sell & retain: Perform outbound calls to promote, upsell + retain loans products based on the leads provided</li><li>Objection handling: Manage and handle customer’s resistance and objections</li><li>Meet sales targets: Achieve & exceed sales target assigned</li><li>Leads management: Maximise conversions within timeline for leads assigned</li><li>Customer Experience: Ensure great customer onboarding journey</li></ul><p><strong>The Talent</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong communication skills</strong> and the ability to handle customer objections</li><li><strong>Sales-driven</strong> & <strong>result oriented</strong> mindset</li><li>Prior Sales experience is a very strong plus</li></ul><p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p><ul><li>Drop your resume and contact us to follow-up, or send your resume to <strong>sarah.ng@adecco.com</strong></li><li>Email Topic: Apply Digital Sales Representative (Telesales | Basic + commissions up to $5k)</li></ul><p>Sarah Ng Mei Wern<br />EA Licence Number: 91C2918<br />Personnel Registration Number: R1983856</p>",
